@startuml
title RecordingViewScreen - Просмотр записи

actor User as User
participant "RecordingViewScreen" as UI
participant "RecordingViewViewModel" as VM
participant "GetEntryByIdUseCase" as UC
participant "DefaultFaultRepository" as REPO
participant "ImageStorage (core)" as IS
participant "EntryDao" as DAO
participant "AppDatabase" as DB

User -> UI: выбирает запись
UI -> VM: onEntrySelected(entryId)
VM -> UC: invoke(entryId)
UC -> REPO: getEntryWithImages(id)
REPO -> DAO: queryEntryWithRelations(id)
DAO -> DB: SELECT entries JOIN images\nON id = entry_id
DB --> DAO: EntryWithImages
DAO --> REPO: EntryWithRecording
REPO --> UC: Result.Success(entry)
UC --> VM: emit State.Success(entry)
VM --> UI: render details + ImageThumbnail list

User -> UI: нажимает на изображение
UI -> VM: onImageClicked(imagePath)
VM -> IS: loadImage(path)
IS --> VM: File/Uri
VM --> UI: open FullScreenImageViewer(image)

@enduml